text: Nikolskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Sterlibashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 70 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Nikolskoye, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
